          <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            The Service may integrate with or link to third-party services (e.g., Google).
            Your use of these services is governed by their respective terms and policies.
            We are not responsible for third-party services or content.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">9. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            THE SERVICE IS PROVIDED "AS IS" AND "AS AVAILABLE" WITHOUT WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND,
            EXPRESS OR IMPLIED. WE DO NOT WARRANT THAT THE SERVICE WILL BE UNINTERRUPTED,
            ERROR-FREE, OR SECURE.
