        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">11. Termination</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            We may terminate or suspend your account at any time for any reason, including
            violation of these terms. You may delete your account at any time. Upon termination,
            your right to use the Service will immediately cease.
